To RunÔºö
Run by calling main.m;
Tasks and instances can be changed through the ‚Äútaskpoint‚Äù flag (20,30,40,50);
The number of iterations can be changed through the ‚ÄúMax_fevs‚Äù flag;
The position coordinates of the robot stations are modified by modifying Rx and Ry, and the coordinates of the task point are modified by modifying Tx and Ty;
The test function ‚ÄúMRTA‚Äù is provided in folder ‚ÄúMM_testfunctions‚Äù;
Note: Before running, the path ‚Äúparams_path‚Äù in the ‚Äúdrl_pop.m‚Äù must be modified. ‚Äúparams_ path‚Äù is the path of the weight file of the deep reinforcement learning model. The weight file ‚Äúactor.pt‚Äù obtained by deep reinforcement learning training is stored in ‚Äútsp_20‚Äù folder.
